Package imagingbook.lib.util

Interface ParameterBundle

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BernsenThresholder.Parameters, BilateralF.Parameters, CannyEdgeDetector.Parameters, DiZenzoCumaniEdgeDetector.Parameters, GradientCornerDetector.Parameters, GrayscaleEdgeDetector.Parameters, HarrisCornerDetector.Parameters, HoughTransformLines.Parameters, InterpolatingThresholder.Parameters, KuwaharaF.Parameters, LucasKanadeMatcher.Parameters, MonochromaticEdgeDetector.Parameters, MopsCornerDetector.Parameters, NiblackThresholder.Parameters, PdfExporter.Parameters, PeronaMalikF.Parameters, SauvolaThresholder.Parameters, ShiTomasiDetector.Parameters, SiftDetector.Parameters, SiftMatcher.Parameters, TschumperleDericheF.Parameters
    public interface ParameterBundle
    Interface to be implemented by local 'Parameters' classes. This is part of the 'simple parameter object' scheme, working with public fields. Only non-static, non-final, public fields are accepted as parameters. Current features: (a) Makes parameter bundles printable by listing all eligible fields. (b) Parameter bundles can be added/modified as a whole by ImageJ's GenericDialog, supported by specific annotations. Use methods addToDialog(GenericDialog) and getFromDialog(GenericDialog). See the example in DemoParameters below. Other functionality may be added in the future.
    Version:
    2022/02/02
